devdoc.details: A decentralized wallet for students to save ETH securely.

deposit().details: Allows users to deposit ETH into the contract. The 'payable' modifier allows the function to receive ETH.

getContractTotalBalance().details: Returns the total balance held by the contract (Owner only hint).

getMyBalance().details: Returns the balance of the caller.

getMyHistory().details: Returns the full transaction history of the caller.

withdraw(uint256).details: Allows users to withdraw their saved ETH.

params._amount: The amount of ETH (in wei) to withdraw.
